    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#CategorizarRequisitosSistema -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#CategorizarRequisitosSistema">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#AtividadeProdutoTrabalho"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:produz rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloEspecificacaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Atividade Produto Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para registrar os requisitos de sistema, recomenda-se categoriz&amp;aacute;-los em requisitos funcionais e requisitos de qualidade ou n&amp;atilde;o funcionais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Os requisitos funcionais&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;devem representar &amp;ldquo;o que o software deve atender&amp;rdquo;, ou seja, as funcionalidades do software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Os requisitos de qualidade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;, tamb&amp;eacute;m conhecidos como requisitos n&amp;atilde;o funcionais, representam as restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do software como, restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es direcionadas ao desempenho, confiabilidade e usabilidade, por exemplo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para registrar requisitos funcionais (RF) e de qualidade (RQ), recomenda-se utilizar um padr&amp;atilde;o para o registro a fim de facilitar a compreens&amp;atilde;o e o mesmo vocabul&amp;aacute;rio pelos membros do time.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Categorizar os requisitos de sistema&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">4</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">3</untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#CenarioEscolhido -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#CenarioEscolhido">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:atendidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PrepararParteCasoUso"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Para tornar o caso de teste execut&amp;aacute;vel, o cen&amp;aacute;rio a ser executado precisa ser selecionado. Uma vez identificado o cen&amp;aacute;rio, o caso de teste &amp;eacute; definido o suficiente para suportar testes explorat&amp;oacute;rios e investigativos. Isso pode ser muito &amp;uacute;til no in&amp;iacute;cio do ciclo de vida do projeto, quando o insight fornecido pelo teste do sistema &amp;eacute; inestim&amp;aacute;vel, mas a especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o (e a solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o) podem n&amp;atilde;o ser est&amp;aacute;veis o suficiente para suportar testes formais e com script.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Para poder executar um caso de teste, um testador deve receber um cen&amp;aacute;rio de teste para executar. A estrutura da narrativa do caso de uso garante que cada fatia do caso de uso apresentar&amp;aacute; ao testador um ou mais cen&amp;aacute;rios de teste candidatos. A arte de criar casos de teste eficazes &amp;eacute; escolher o subconjunto certo de poss&amp;iacute;veis cen&amp;aacute;rios de teste para cumprir a ideia de teste e definir claramente o que est&amp;aacute; &amp;ldquo;pronto&amp;rdquo; para a fatia.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Espera-se que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;O cen&amp;aacute;rio a ser executado est&amp;aacute; claramente definido.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;O estado inicial e final da execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do cen&amp;aacute;rio s&amp;atilde;o definidos. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cen&amp;aacute;rio escolhido&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ClassificarRelacionamentoRastreabilReq -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ClassificarRelacionamentoRastreabilReq">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloRastreabilidade"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;A rastreabilidade de requisitos prop&amp;otilde;e as seguintes categorias e deve ser definida junto &amp;agrave; finalidade &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;(POHL; RUPP 2015); (REINEHR 2018); (&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;VAZQUEZ; &amp;nbsp;SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Rastreabilidade pr&amp;eacute;-especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos ou rastreabilidade para tr&amp;aacute;s (backward traceability):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Consiste no relacionamento de rastreabilidade entre requisitos os artefatos que apoiam a atividade de requisitos, como exemplo, artefatos como a fonte ou a origem de um requisito (artefatos pr&amp;eacute;vios).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Rastreabilidade p&amp;oacute;s-especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos ou rastreabilidade para frente (forward traceability):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Envolve as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de rastreabilidade entre requisitos e artefatos resultantes de atividades subsequentes de desenvolvimento. Como exemplos de artefatos, podem ser componentes, implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ou casos de testes, associados a um requisito.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Rastreabilidade entre requisitos, tamb&amp;eacute;m chamada de rastreabilidade vertical:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Considera o mapeamento de depend&amp;ecirc;ncias entre requisitos. Como exemplo, destaca-se a rastreabilidade voltada &amp;agrave; informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que um requisito refina, generaliza ou substitui outro requisito.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 1: Exemplo 1 de pr&amp;eacute; e p&amp;oacute;s-rastreabilidade dos requisitos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#0c343d;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:396px;height:181px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0c343d;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXf2lwIdmkDprUArXh7asavW546nyXki3DDxtoqS8Mo7-kZlsPb0LzBvTuQubMDN41b9jEPsHFbzQHv8H1EspA3QyswuHAlBsSteBA7dEiBq3H-r6beuc5xURyMNn2usMEjKnXIRY-ak1--FypWB0ji3c4of?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;396&quot; height=&quot;181&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Reinehr, 2018&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 2: Exemplo 2 de pr&amp;eacute; e p&amp;oacute;s-rastreabilidade dos requisitos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:326px;height:154px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color:#ffffff;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeMzWoRNzZbfHQcv-mI6e-uCeIO1kXuZRZrcNZasMrsnZiAR1XrrZTymx0IhoRSHm5wvO5fSFu7ko-mA-HeZk1p9VvMAMwuuT9udEIx6BUihn9tHgotBTieyQ89asgqLdCP2G7dUfKtSUXZdX0nd1HC9jHM?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;326&quot; height=&quot;154&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Vazquez &amp;amp; Sim&amp;otilde;es, 2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-indent: 36pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;No contexto da classifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do relacionamento de rastreabilidade, &amp;eacute; poss&amp;iacute;vel vincul&amp;aacute;-los &amp;agrave; rastreabilidade horizontal ou vertical.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: 36pt;&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Rastreabilidade Horizontal:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Recomenda-se quando deseja-se estabelecer v&amp;iacute;nculos entre as vers&amp;otilde;es diferentes de requisitos ou artefatos em determinada fase do ciclo de vida do projeto, ou, ainda, quando pretende-se vincular requisitos e artefatos que est&amp;atilde;o em um mesmo n&amp;iacute;vel&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 8px;&apos;&gt;(VAZQUEZ; SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 3: Exemplo de rastreabilidade horizontal entre vers&amp;otilde;es do mesmo artefato&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#0c343d;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:287px;height:137px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0c343d;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXdMT3_u4vgoQqN__b-azzm449VQ2lu8aRq832Von0OB_H4jiK9FlyvIbDfIjP07SjrJv7vPM5T8hfBvQqa-sy9RjXnuQdDL7kUaVuOFQBCFrLgUWXdrAJRD7VXcT_uUQq2FYZILj8o5bdTeIr_FtR7sMSg?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;287&quot; height=&quot;137&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Vazquez &amp;amp; Sim&amp;otilde;es, 2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;margin-left: 36pt;&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Rastreabilidade Vertical:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Sugere-se a rastreabilidade vertical quando pretende-se estabelecer v&amp;iacute;nculos entre requisitos ou artefatos que est&amp;atilde;o em diferentes fases do ciclo de vida do projeto&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;(VAZQUEZ; SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 4: Exemplo de rastreabilidade vertical entre requisitos e artefatos produzidos em diferentes fases do projeto&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#0c343d;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:243px;height:188px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0c343d;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfgd8RUf_z6vJ_0gyHeUdBmaDhWG86LMAwrn5A73gko48gHqiToRfjCElmTSSd8uAqJgf2i8dI-0RVw6i3gyC-HE738TZpuR5iFNG6a2AVXzS73DTtCSmRzOGhxqi0UfqROpP08g6-j0ACuZdzYWwoPmAoy?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;243&quot; height=&quot;188&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Vazquez &amp;amp; Sim&amp;otilde;es, 2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 14px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Classificar o relacionamento de rastreabilidade de requisitos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ColetarConsolidarProblemas -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ColetarConsolidarProblemas">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#AtividadeProdutoTrabalho"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:produz rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloRevisaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Atividade Produto Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Durante a coleta de falhas, todas as falhas identificadas devem ser coletadas, consolidadas e registradas. O momento de consolida&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o sinaliza falhas que foram detectadas v&amp;aacute;rias vezes, assim como falhas que n&amp;atilde;o caracterizam erro. Este &amp;uacute;ltimo caso pode acontecer quando um revisor interpretar de forma equivocada um requisito ou alguma restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o sobre ele.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Na consolida&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o tamb&amp;eacute;m devem ser registradas, al&amp;eacute;m das falhas e erros, as medidas corretivas sugeridas (Pohl; Rupp 2015). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Coletar e consolidar os problemas&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">4</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">3</untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ComScriptAutomatizado -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ComScriptAutomatizado">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:atendidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PrepararParteCasoUso"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Se um caso de teste for usado muitas vezes ou para suportar muitos testes diferentes, ent&amp;atilde;o vale a pena fazer um esfor&amp;ccedil;o para criar um script completo ou automatiz&amp;aacute;-lo.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Para que um caso de teste seja totalmente roteirizado e automatiz&amp;aacute;vel, ele n&amp;atilde;o deve conter ambiguidade. Nesse n&amp;iacute;vel de detalhe, o caso de teste &amp;eacute; frequentemente documentado como um script de teste automatizado, que pode ser interpretado e executado por uma ferramenta de teste automatizado.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Espera-se que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Os dados de teste est&amp;atilde;o dispon&amp;iacute;veis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Todas as etapas do caso de teste s&amp;atilde;o definidas e programadas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;N&amp;atilde;o h&amp;aacute; instru&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es amb&amp;iacute;guas, etapas de navega&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, valores de entrada ou resultados esperados.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;O caso de teste pode ser executado sem qualquer interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ou tomada de decis&amp;atilde;o adicional.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Se for totalmente automatizado, um script de teste automatizado estar&amp;aacute; dispon&amp;iacute;vel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Com script ou automatizado&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">5</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
