    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DefinicaoTecnicasER -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DefinicaoTecnicasER">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#OrientacoesER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ap&amp;oacute;s identificar as fontes de requisitos, o engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos pode iniciar a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, por&amp;eacute;m, os requisitos apresentados s&amp;atilde;o elicitados prontos e completos. O engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos formula os requisitos a partir das informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es solicitadas inicialmente.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para realizar a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos s&amp;atilde;o propostas diferentes t&amp;eacute;cnicas para obter informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de requisitos relevantes para defini-los corretamente. No entanto, algumas t&amp;eacute;cnicas funcionam melhor com certas classes de stakeholders do que outras&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt; .&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, por vezes, &amp;eacute; uma tarefa dif&amp;iacute;cil, pois os stakeholders podem ter dificuldade em relacionar ou descrever suas tarefas, esquecendo informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es importantes ou deixando de relat&amp;aacute;-las propositalmente. Nessa perspectiva, o engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos deve ter a sensibilidade de identificar poss&amp;iacute;veis conflitos de interesse e articular a comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de forma que possibilite obter informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es claras, relevantes e corretas&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Tentando tornar a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos espec&amp;iacute;ficos, podem ser combinadas v&amp;aacute;rias t&amp;eacute;cnicas de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, conforme a necessidade do projeto e do contexto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Dentre as t&amp;eacute;cnicas que podem ser definidas para a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, destacam-se:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Entrevistas:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Entrevistar as partes interessadas &amp;eacute; um meio &amp;ldquo;tradicional&amp;rdquo; de elicitar requisitos. &amp;Eacute; importante entender as vantagens e limita&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es das entrevistas e como elas devem ser conduzidas &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Hist&amp;oacute;rias de usu&amp;aacute;rio&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;: E&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;ssa t&amp;eacute;cnica &amp;eacute; comumente usada em m&amp;eacute;todos &amp;aacute;geis e se refere &amp;agrave;s especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e de alto n&amp;iacute;vel da funcionalidade necess&amp;aacute;ria expressa em termos do cliente. Uma hist&amp;oacute;ria de usu&amp;aacute;rio t&amp;iacute;pica tem o formato: &amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Como &amp;lt;fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;gt;, eu quero &amp;lt;objetivo/desejo&amp;gt; para que &amp;lt;benef&amp;iacute;cio&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Cen&amp;aacute;rios de uso:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Os cen&amp;aacute;rios fornecem um meio interessante e detalhado para fornecer contexto para a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos requisitos do usu&amp;aacute;rio. Permitimos que o engenheiro de software forne&amp;ccedil;a uma estrutura para perguntas sobre tarefas do usu&amp;aacute;rio, permitindo que perguntas do tipo &amp;ldquo;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;e se&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;rdquo; e &amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;como isso &amp;eacute; feito&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;rdquo; sejam realizadas. O tipo mais comum de cen&amp;aacute;rio &amp;eacute; a descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do caso de uso&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;SOMMERVILLE 2018)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o (Etnografia):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A import&amp;acirc;ncia do contexto do software dentro do ambiente organizacional levou &amp;agrave; adapta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de t&amp;eacute;cnicas observacionais, como a etnografia, para a obten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos. Engenheiros de software aprendem sobre as tarefas do usu&amp;aacute;rio emergindo no ambiente e observando como os usu&amp;aacute;rios realizam suas tarefas, interagem entre si e com ferramentas de software e outros recursos&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SOMMERVILLE 2018)&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Prototipagem de interface de usu&amp;aacute;rio de baixa ou alta fidelidade&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Esta t&amp;eacute;cnica &amp;eacute; uma ferramenta poderosa para requisitos claros amb&amp;iacute;guos, ausentes ou conflitantes. Fornecemos aos usu&amp;aacute;rios um contexto dentro do qual eles podem entender melhor quais informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es precisam fornecer por meio de prot&amp;oacute;tipos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Reuni&amp;otilde;es, incluindo brainstorming:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;O objetivo dessas reuni&amp;otilde;es &amp;eacute; proporcionar um efeito somativo, por meio do qual um grupo de pessoas pode apresentar mais insights sobre seus requisitos de software que trabalham individualmente. Podem um brainstorming e refinar ideias dif&amp;iacute;ceis de trazer &amp;agrave; tona usando entrevistas&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2024)&lt;/span&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
