    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DescritoResumidamente -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DescritoResumidamente">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:atendidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#EcontrarAtoreseUC"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;O n&amp;iacute;vel de detalhe mais leve que captura apenas o objetivo do caso de uso e qual ator o inicia.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Este n&amp;iacute;vel de detalhe &amp;eacute; adequado para casos de uso que n&amp;atilde;o foram selecionados imediatamente para implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Ser&amp;atilde;o necess&amp;aacute;rios mais detalhes se o caso de uso for dividido para implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Espera-se que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;O caso de uso seja nomeado.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Possua uma breve descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o curta e informativa.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Descrito resumidamente&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">1</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DesenvolverModelagemRequisitos -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DesenvolverModelagemRequisitos">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#AtividadeProdutoTrabalho"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:produz rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloEspecificacaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Atividade Produto Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A modelagem de requisitos pode ser representada por diferentes artefatos, os quais poder&amp;atilde;o ser desenvolvidos conforme a necessidade da organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o em representar seu projeto de software ou parte dele.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dentre os artefatos para especificar os requisitos, sugere-se:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Behavior Driven Development (BDD):&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;BDD caracteriza-se como desenvolvimento baseado em comportamento e consiste em uma abordagem de desenvolvimento colaborativo na qual, os times usam conversas estruturadas sobre exemplos e contraexemplos de regras de neg&amp;oacute;cios e o comportamento esperado para construir um entendimento avan&amp;ccedil;ado e compartilhado dos recursos que beneficiar&amp;atilde;o os usu&amp;aacute;rios e o neg&amp;oacute;cio de modo geral (Smart; Molak 2023).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Normalmente esses exemplos s&amp;atilde;o expressos em um formato execut&amp;aacute;vel que atua como base para crit&amp;eacute;rios e testes de aceita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o automatizados que validam o comportamento do software (Alferez et al. 2019).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda-se o uso da linguagem Gherkin para representar o BDD:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Dado-Quando-Ent&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Dado&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;[contexto inicial]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;[evento ou a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o]&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;[resultado esperado], conforme observa-se no exemplo a seguir&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Smart; Molak 2023)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;ldquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Dado que&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;h&amp;aacute; dinheiro suficiente na minha conta&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;eu fa&amp;ccedil;o um saque&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ent&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;eu recebo a quantia esperada de dinheiro do caixa eletr&amp;ocirc;nico&amp;rdquo; (Alferez et al. 2019).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos cen&amp;aacute;rios de casos de uso:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Os casos de uso s&amp;atilde;o uma t&amp;eacute;cnica para captar os requisitos funcionais de um sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:circle;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Servem para descrever as intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es t&amp;iacute;picas entre os usu&amp;aacute;rios de um sistema e o pr&amp;oacute;prio sistema, fornecendo uma narrativa sobre como o sistema &amp;eacute; utilizado.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:circle;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um cen&amp;aacute;rio &amp;eacute; uma sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia de passos que descreve uma intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre um usu&amp;aacute;rio e um sistema. Assim, se tivermos uma loja on-line baseada na Web (loja virtual), poderia ter um cen&amp;aacute;rio de Compra de um Produto que descreve:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:square;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;ldquo;O cliente navega no cat&amp;aacute;logo de itens e adiciona os itens desejados &amp;agrave; sua cesta de compras. Quando o cliente deseja pagar, descreve o endere&amp;ccedil;o de entrega, fornece as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do cart&amp;atilde;o de cr&amp;eacute;dito e confirma a venda. O sistema verifica a autoriza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do cart&amp;atilde;o de cr&amp;eacute;dito e confirma a venda imediatamente e com um e-mail subsequente&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Cada caso de uso tem um ator principal, que pede ao sistema para que execute um servi&amp;ccedil;o. Podem existir outros atores com os quais o sistema se comunica enquanto executa o caso de uso, conhecidos como atores secund&amp;aacute;rios.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um ator &amp;eacute; um papel que um usu&amp;aacute;rio desempenha com rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ao sistema. Os atores podem ser o cliente, representante de servi&amp;ccedil;o ao cliente, gerente de vendas e analista de produto. Os atores realizam os casos de uso.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um ator n&amp;atilde;o precisa ser um ser humano.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&quot;list-style-type:disc;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Se o sistema realiza um servi&amp;ccedil;o para outro sistema de computador, esse outro sistema &amp;eacute; um ator.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Cada passo em um caso de uso, &amp;eacute; um elemento da intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre um ator e o sistema.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Deve ser uma declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o simples mostrando claramente quem est&amp;aacute; executando o passo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O passo deve apresentar a inten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do ator e n&amp;atilde;o os mecanismos do que o ator faz.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma extens&amp;atilde;o dentro do caso de uso nomeia uma condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que resulta em diferentes intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es daquelas descritas no cen&amp;aacute;rio principal de sucesso e informa quais s&amp;atilde;o essas diferen&amp;ccedil;as.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Iniciar a extens&amp;atilde;o dando um nome ao passo em que a condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; detectada e fornecer uma breve descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ap&amp;oacute;s a condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, enumerar os passos, no mesmo estilo que o do cen&amp;aacute;rio principal de sucesso.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Concluir esses passos descrevendo onde retorna para o cen&amp;aacute;rio principal de sucesso, caso retorne.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 1: Exemplo de descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de cen&amp;aacute;rio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXcdcMAR6NFpQAVmrzZlsvpwdXtMR-HyvuvgMMxZo1LBYskmZyJk57540FIdSwlwTVsHJPeAKaxMDVGEXmTOYK3nlhz_c_pk3yawMRhvPAQJIYALyYf8_qV4Ts7K4kagLTzgd_fCj0G5XRqI777_A1IIpdhS?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;280&quot; height=&quot;168&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Fowler, 2007&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Para representar a especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos recomenda-se os seguintes artefatos, conforme a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(47, 47, 47); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unified Modeling Language&amp;trade; (UML&amp;reg;):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px;&apos;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Diagrama de casos de uso:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;O diagrama de casos de uso &amp;eacute; uma t&amp;eacute;cnica para captar os requisitos funcionais de um sistema. Eles servem para descrever as intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es t&amp;iacute;picas entre os usu&amp;aacute;rios de um sistema e o pr&amp;oacute;prio sistema, fornecendo uma narrativa sobre como o sistema &amp;eacute; utilizado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;A melhor maneira de pensar um diagrama de caso de uso &amp;eacute; como um sum&amp;aacute;rio gr&amp;aacute;fico do conjunto de casos de uso.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;O diagrama de casos de uso mostra os atores, os casos de uso e os relacionamentos entre eles:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Quais atores realizam quais casos de uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Quais casos de uso incluem outros casos de uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Os casos de uso s&amp;atilde;o uma ferramenta valiosa para ajudar no entendimento dos requisitos funcionais de um sistema.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Uma primeira passagem nos casos de uso deve ser feita no in&amp;iacute;cio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Vers&amp;otilde;es mais detalhadas dos casos de uso devem ser elaboradas apenas antes do desenvolvimento desse caso de uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 2: Exemplo de diagrama de caso de uso&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXeyhML7gr4iTExkJRL604U-CTSEi1uOn3a6FvJm3NwQ3p_13j0uXBvoTn44p7qsQurhQzv32_zAv79ZkDOg_UMhVF7Q763eqAkEN4hCuPN6VOH7e6AvJTF-HSMJtCPvw0ixLN27YHGy41CpfJxl5z67PAA?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;246&quot; height=&quot;164&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Fonte: Fowler, 2007&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px;&apos;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Diagrama de atividades:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 14px;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Os diagramas de atividades s&amp;atilde;o uma t&amp;eacute;cnica para descrever a l&amp;oacute;gica de procedimento, processo de neg&amp;oacute;cio e fluxo de trabalho.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;O diagrama de atividades permite que quem est&amp;aacute; seguindo o processo escolha a ordem na qual fazer as coisas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Ele simplesmente determina as regras essenciais de sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia que se deve seguir.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;3&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Isso &amp;eacute; importante para modelagem de neg&amp;oacute;cios, pois os processos frequentemente ocorrem em paralelo.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.38;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;A maior qualidade dos diagramas de atividades est&amp;aacute; no fato de que eles suportam e estimulam o comportamento paralelo. Isso os torna uma excelente ferramenta para modelagem de fluxos de trabalho e de processos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
