        <untitled-ontology-3:apresentacao>&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Uma pr&amp;aacute;tica escal&amp;aacute;vel e &amp;aacute;gil que utiliza casos de uso para capturar um conjunto de requisitos e impulsionar o desenvolvimento incremental de um sistema para atend&amp;ecirc;-los.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Usar esta pr&amp;aacute;tica para capturar requisitos de uma forma acess&amp;iacute;vel e impulsionar o desenvolvimento de software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/images/cards/practice/Use%20Case%202.0%20Essentials_Overview.png?t=1541069334899&quot; usemap=&quot;#use_case_20_essentialsOverview_map&quot; style=&quot;border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;map name=&quot;use_case_20_essentialsOverview_map&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;5,10,99,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_-qQEAjX4EeG4rrZ-ZoAVmA/Use-Case%20Model_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;A model that captures and visualizes all of the useful ways to use a system.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;104,10,198,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_bwhEYSyJEeGkkOC4K2RI6A/Find%20Actors%20and%20Use%20Cases_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Agree on the goals and value of the system by identifying ways of using and testing it.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;203,10,297,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_iMVRQSyJEeGkkOC4K2RI6A/Slice%20the%20Use%20Cases_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Identify Use-Case Slices based on Use Cases to aid implementation.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;302,10,396,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_m71tUSyJEeGkkOC4K2RI6A/Prepare%20a%20Use-Case%20Slice_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;A Use-Case Slice is prepared for development by elaborating its narrative and test cases.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;401,10,495,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_D7oxEUFdEeG1ZNmea40YGw/Analyze%20a%20Use-Case%20Slice_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Analyze the impact of a Use-Case slice and shape its implementation. (May be skipped if the implementation is trivial).&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;500,10,594,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_l6jqcUFZEeG1ZNmea40YGw/Inspect%20and%20Adapt%20the%20Use%20Cases_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Handle change and track progress by tuning the use-case model, use cases and use-case slices.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;599,10,693,112&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_IXqYEDb3EeGqV8_a7z_HbA/Use%20Case_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;All the ways of using a system to achieve a particular goal for a particular user.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;5,122,99,224&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_QK2AgDb3EeGqV8_a7z_HbA/Use-Case%20Slice_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;One or more stories selected from a use case to form a work item that is of clear value to the customer.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;104,122,198,224&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_8zGZMjd5EeG1cOrViFGY9w/Use-Case%20Narrative_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Tells the story of how the system and its actors work together to achieve a particular goal.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;203,122,297,224&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_YtQeYj4GEeGsI6HKv3Dk0A/Use-Case%20Realization_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Shows how the system’s elements, such as components, programs, stored procedures, configuration files and data-base tables, collaborate to perform a use case.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;302,122,396,224&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/_NUyfwjb_EeG_i5kjlgR0Sw/Supporting%20Information_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Captures important terms used to describe the system, and any and all requirements that don’t fit inside the use-case model.&quot;&gt;&lt;area shape=&quot;rect&quot; coords=&quot;401,122,495,224&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/html/3d647cb4-f285-4961-bc80-a02c40168c5e/Use%20Case%20Test%20Case_gd.html&quot; title=&quot;Defines test inputs and expected results to help evaluate whether a system works correctly. * There can be one or more Test Cases to verify each Use-Case Slice.&quot;&gt;&lt;/map&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);font-size: 11px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;Fonte:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a data-fr-linked=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/content/use-case-20-essentials-publication&quot;&gt;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/content/use-case-20-essentials-publication&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;(JACOBSON 2017)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 2.375em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:apresentacao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:classificacaoPratica>Específica</untitled-ontology-3:classificacaoPratica>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Elaborar artefatos da Linguagem de Modelagem Unificada (UML) - Modelo de Caso de Uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:fluxoAtividades>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Fluxo de atividades&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A Pr&amp;aacute;tica do Caso de Uso deve ser usada quando as equipes pretendem:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;A pr&amp;aacute;tica do caso de Uso come&amp;ccedil;a identificando atores e casos de uso e selecionando e priorizando as partes (fatias) dos casos de uso a serem desenvolvidos.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;A pr&amp;aacute;tica continua detalhando as fatias dos casos de uso e, mais importante, os casos de teste necess&amp;aacute;rios para verificar cada fatia. O foco ent&amp;atilde;o muda para a implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de software para passar nos casos de teste. A pr&amp;aacute;tica termina acompanhando o progresso em termos de software verificado e funcionando e retroalimentando os resultados para lidar com as mudan&amp;ccedil;as e apoiar melhor a equipe.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/sites/default/files/embedded-practices/Use_Case_2.0_Essentials_HTML_guidelines6/images/uc2_activity_flow2.png&quot; usemap=&quot;#map_activity_flow&quot; style=&quot;text-align: start; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; border: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px; color: rgb(204, 204, 204);&quot;&gt;Fonte: &lt;a data-fr-linked=&quot;true&quot; href=&quot;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/content/use-case-20-essentials-publication&quot;&gt;https://practicelibrary.ivarjacobson.com/content/use-case-20-essentials-publication&lt;/a&gt; (JABOBSON 2017)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:fluxoAtividades>
