        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O Grafo de rastreabilidade &amp;eacute; constru&amp;iacute;do considerando os tipos de relacionamentos para cada tipo de artefato a serem rastreados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;No entanto, o grafo deve ser preenchido quando todos os requisitos forem negociados e acordados com o cliente no in&amp;iacute;cio do ciclo de desenvolvimento de software&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(KECHI, 2011)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
