    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ExecucaoER -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ExecucaoER">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PadraoOrientacoesRegistroER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Durante a execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o das atividades de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, o foco &amp;eacute; coletar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es proativamente junto aos stakeholders utilizando as t&amp;eacute;cnicas de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o definidas na prepara&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A metodologia e caracter&amp;iacute;sticas de cada t&amp;eacute;cnica devem ser observadas e consideradas, pois cada t&amp;eacute;cnica tem suas especificidades.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da t&amp;eacute;cnica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(VAZQUEZ; SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Durante a execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da t&amp;eacute;cnica, evitar o desvio do escopo do projeto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O projeto nem sempre tem o objetivo de resolver todos os problemas relatados pelos stakeholders, pois alguns podem estar fora do escopo do projeto, por isso, &amp;eacute; importante conscientizar os stakeholders do objetivo do projeto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Manter a rastreabilidade dos requisitos dos stakeholders para os requisitos de neg&amp;oacute;cios, pois &amp;eacute; a garantia que o escopo do projeto n&amp;atilde;o ser&amp;aacute; desviado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ficar atento para capturar os atributos dos requisitos, os quais podem ser apoiados e identificados seguindo o plano de gerenciamento de requisitos. Exemplos de atributos: origem, prioridade, autor, propriet&amp;aacute;rio, estado, risco, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Na captura dos requisitos e seus atributos deve-se utilizar um mecanismo para registro dessas informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, como anot&amp;aacute;-las em um papel, documento, ferramenta, gravar (desde que autorizado pelos stakeholders).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;N&amp;atilde;o esperar que a parte interessada relate tudo o que &amp;eacute; necess&amp;aacute;rio para atender o escopo do projeto, voluntariamente. Requisitos impl&amp;iacute;citos, como a omiss&amp;atilde;o de requisitos fundamentais, ocasionados pela falta de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es por parte dos stakeholders, &amp;eacute; um problema que ocorre durante a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. O papel do analista &amp;eacute; fundamental nesses momentos, pois deve ter sensibilidade e expertise para identificar o que a parte interessada pensa que &amp;eacute; &amp;oacute;bvio e n&amp;atilde;o menciona. Isso evitar&amp;aacute; retrabalho &amp;agrave; frente no projeto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Deve haver tempo e recurso para que o analista amplie ou melhore seu conhecimento do neg&amp;oacute;cio. Para isso, sugere-se organizar as partes de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o coletadas em diferentes vis&amp;otilde;es visando identificar lacunas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para a documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos requisitos da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o durante a execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(VAZQUEZ; SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;As t&amp;eacute;cnicas adotadas durante a execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, definem o tipo de documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;H&amp;aacute; abordagens em que os produtos da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o s&amp;atilde;o produtos finais, como as hist&amp;oacute;rias de usu&amp;aacute;rios adotadas nos m&amp;eacute;todos &amp;aacute;geis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Abordagens em que os produtos da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o s&amp;atilde;o requisitos intermedi&amp;aacute;rios, a fim de registrar decis&amp;otilde;es sobre assuntos, at&amp;eacute; ent&amp;atilde;o, pendentes, devem documentar por meio de atas de reuni&amp;otilde;es, relat&amp;oacute;rios, registro de &amp;aacute;udio ou v&amp;iacute;deo, quadro de anota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, por exemplo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Nesse caso, esse tipo de documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ser&amp;aacute; utilizado para confirmar a compreens&amp;atilde;o do analista com os stakeholders sobre as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es coletadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Devem ser registradas tamb&amp;eacute;m, quest&amp;otilde;es em aberto e d&amp;uacute;vidas que surgiram durante essas cerim&amp;ocirc;nias e que n&amp;atilde;o foram esclarecidas at&amp;eacute; ent&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ExecucaoRevReq -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ExecucaoRevReq">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloRevisaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No n&amp;iacute;vel de execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, os revisores procuram por falhas nos requisitos, apoiadas no artefato que est&amp;aacute; sendo revisado, por exemplo, diagrama de caso de uso, documento de especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, etc. A revis&amp;atilde;o pode ser realizada individualmente por cada revisor, parte dos revisores ou pelo time todo.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Durante o n&amp;iacute;vel de execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, todas as falhas devem ser registradas para serem corrigidas posteriormente e, para isso, recomenda-se registrar as seguintes informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Nome do revisor e seu papel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Artefato revisado, sua vers&amp;atilde;o,o projeto ao qual est&amp;aacute; vinculado e vers&amp;atilde;o do projeto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Registro de falhas: Para cada falha, informar a descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da falha, a localiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da falha no artefato, a p&amp;aacute;gina, quando houver, e o tipo de falha - omiss&amp;atilde;o, ambiguidade&amp;hellip;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informar as depend&amp;ecirc;ncias: Por exemplo: Se o artefato revisado for um diagrama de caso de uso, pode informar as depend&amp;ecirc;ncias ou refer&amp;ecirc;ncias daquele caso de uso como os requisitos funcionais e n&amp;atilde;o funcionais associados a ele.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Data da revis&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Estimativa de esfo&amp;ccedil;o prevista inicialmente para a revis&amp;atilde;o e o esfor&amp;ccedil;o real dedicado &amp;agrave; revis&amp;atilde;o. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O esfor&amp;ccedil;o pode ser apresentado em horas, minutos ou dia, por&amp;eacute;m, &amp;eacute; preciso padronizar.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


