    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#FechamentoRevReq -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#FechamentoRevReq">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloRevisaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No n&amp;iacute;vel de fechamento da revis&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, os revisores se re&amp;uacute;nem para compartilharem e analisarem suas revis&amp;otilde;es observando os registros individuais de problemas - semelhantes ou n&amp;atilde;o, &amp;nbsp;para unific&amp;aacute;-los posteriormente.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ap&amp;oacute;s essa confer&amp;ecirc;ncia, os revisores sintetizam as falhas em um &amp;uacute;nico registro e simplificam as redund&amp;acirc;ncias de registros dos problemas identificados nas revis&amp;otilde;es individuais.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Para o registro de fechamento, recomenda-se manter as seguintes informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, destacadas na execu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Nome e papel dos revisores.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Artefato revisado, sua vers&amp;atilde;o e o projeto ao qual est&amp;aacute; vinculado e vers&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Registro de problema: Para cada problema, informar a descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do problema, a localiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do problema no artefato, a p&amp;aacute;gina, quando houver e o tipo de falha - omiss&amp;atilde;o, ambiguidade&amp;hellip;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informar as depend&amp;ecirc;ncias: Por exemplo: Se o artefato revisado for um diagrama de caso de uso, pode informar as depend&amp;ecirc;ncias ou refer&amp;ecirc;ncias daquele caso de uso como os requisitos funcionais e n&amp;atilde;o funcionais associados a ele.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Medidas corretivas para os problemas identificados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Data do fechamento da revis&amp;atilde;o de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Estimativa de esfor&amp;ccedil;o total considerando os revisores envolvidos e o esfor&amp;ccedil;o real.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O esfor&amp;ccedil;o pode ser apresentado em horas, minutos ou dia, por&amp;eacute;m, &amp;eacute; preciso padronizar.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fechamento da revis&amp;atilde;o de requisitos&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">3</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


