        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#CasoTestePB"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;O racioc&amp;iacute;nio que justifica o caso de teste foi formulado, incluindo por que o caso de teste existe e qual aspecto ou parte dos requisitos deve ser testado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Espera-se que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;Os principais itens que precisamos testar foram documentados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;As ideias de teste cobrem os cen&amp;aacute;rios de uso que devem ser suportados para atingir o valor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-align: left;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 14.4px;&quot;&gt;As partes interessadas est&amp;atilde;o satisfeitas porque as ideias de teste juntas verificam uma implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o aceit&amp;aacute;vel do item a ser implementado. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
