            &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Os requisitos de software s&amp;atilde;o frequentemente escritos em linguagem natural, mas, na concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos de software, isso pode ser complementado por especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es formais ou semiformais.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
        &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;A sele&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es mencionadas permite que requisitos espec&amp;iacute;ficos e aspectos da arquitetura de software sejam descritos de forma mais precisa e concisa do que a linguagem natural.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
        &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Os requisitos de usu&amp;aacute;rio &amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
                &lt;/font&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;devem ser identificados e registrados sob essa perspectiva.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
                &lt;/font&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Os requisitos do sistema&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
                &lt;/font&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;s&amp;atilde;o vers&amp;otilde;es expandidas dos requisitos do usu&amp;aacute;rio e incluem detalhes e explicam como os requisitos do usu&amp;aacute;rio devem ser fornecidos pelo sistema.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
                &lt;/font&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                            &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;Eles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;
                        &lt;/font&gt;
                    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;
                            &lt;font style=&quot;vertical-align: inherit;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;ser&amp;atilde;o usados como parte do contrato para a implementa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do sistema e devem, portanto, ser uma previs&amp;atilde;o completa e espec&amp;iacute;fica de todo o sistema.&lt;/font&gt;
                        &lt;/font&gt;
                    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
