        <untitled-ontology-3:contem rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#Planejada"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:contem rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#Realizada"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eOrganizadoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ItemArtefatoRastreado"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eOrganizadoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RelacionamentoItensArtefatos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProduzidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#AcompanharManterRastreabilidadeRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProduzidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PlanejarRastreabilidadeRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProduzidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RealizarRastreabilidadeRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Produto de Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Matriz de rastreabilidade&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;T&amp;eacute;cnica que facilita a visualiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da rastreabilidade documentada entre requisitos&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;versus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;requisitos e requisitos&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;versus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;outros itens. Na matriz, incluem-se os itens rastreados nos eixos de uma tabela e marcam-se os pontos de interse&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;VAZQUEZ; &amp;nbsp;SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Caso o projeto tenha poucos requisitos, uma tabela ou planilha normalmente &amp;eacute; suficiente. Por&amp;eacute;m, se o projeto manter um grande volume de requisitos, recomenda-se usar uma ferramenta especializada, pois uma planilha &amp;eacute; invi&amp;aacute;vel para atender o esfor&amp;ccedil;o da manuten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o na rastreabilidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;A matriz serve de atividade complementar &amp;agrave;s an&amp;aacute;lises de impactos das mudan&amp;ccedil;as de requisitos solicitadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-indent: 36pt;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;Uma matriz de rastreabilidade possui &amp;nbsp;linhas e colunas:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;As linhas da matriz de rastreabilidade s&amp;atilde;o rotuladas com os nomes dos requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;As colunas podem ser rotuladas com o nome de um outro artefato da engenharia de software, como &amp;nbsp;um elemento do projeto ou um caso de teste.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;A presen&amp;ccedil;a de um v&amp;iacute;nculo (relacionamento) entre os dois artefatos &amp;eacute; sinalizada na c&amp;eacute;lula da matriz.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;1&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;As matrizes de rastreabilidade podem ser usadas para garantir que os artefatos de engenharia considerem todos os requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:8pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Figura 1: Exemplo 1 de matriz de &amp;nbsp;rastreabilidade entre requisitos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
