&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;sup style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;PRESSMAN, Roger S.; MAXIM, Bruce R. Engenharia de software. 9th ed. Porto Alegre: AMGH, 2021.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;sup style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;SWEBOK. Guide to the Software Engineering Body of Knowledge v4.0. Editors: Hironori Washizaki, Waseda University (IEEE Computer Society 2024 President-Elect, 2025 President). 2024.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:referenciaRE>
