        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Produto de Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Narrativa de caso de uso&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Descreva as hist&amp;oacute;rias usadas para explorar os requisitos e identificar as fatias dos casos de uso.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Descreva uma sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia de a&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, incluindo variantes, que um Sistema de Software e seus atores podem realizar para atingir um objetivo.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;S&amp;atilde;o apresentados como um conjunto de fluxos.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Capture as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de requisitos necess&amp;aacute;rias para conduzir as atividades de desenvolvimento.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;As narrativas de casos de uso podem ser capturadas de muitas maneiras diferentes; como parte de um Wiki, em fichas, como documentos do Microsoft Word ou usando uma das muitas ferramentas de gerenciamento de trabalho, gerenciamento de requisitos ou modelagem visual dispon&amp;iacute;veis comercialmente.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;A narrativa de casos de uso &amp;eacute; um produto de trabalho muito flex&amp;iacute;vel que pode ser expandido para capturar a quantidade de detalhes necess&amp;aacute;ria para ter sucesso, independentemente das circunst&amp;acirc;ncias.&amp;nbsp;Se voc&amp;ecirc; faz parte de uma pequena equipe que trabalha em colabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o cliente em um projeto explorat&amp;oacute;rio, os esbo&amp;ccedil;os com marcadores fornecem uma abordagem muito leve para descobrir os requisitos.&amp;nbsp;Se voc&amp;ecirc; estiver trabalhando em um ambiente mais r&amp;iacute;gido, onde h&amp;aacute; pouco acesso aos verdadeiros especialistas, ent&amp;atilde;o esbo&amp;ccedil;os essenciais ou narrativas totalmente descritas podem ser usados para preencher as lacunas no conhecimento da equipe.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Nem toda narrativa de casos de uso precisa ser levada ao mesmo n&amp;iacute;vel de detalhe; n&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; incomum que os casos de uso mais importantes e arriscados sejam mais detalhados que os outros. O mesmo vale para as se&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es da narrativa do caso de uso; as partes mais importantes, complexas ou arriscadas de um caso de uso s&amp;atilde;o frequentemente descritas com mais detalhes do que as outras.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es adicionais&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Conte&amp;uacute;do essencial&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1 Nome: O nome do caso de uso. Utilize um nome, composto por um verbo e um substantivo, que descreva o resultado alcan&amp;ccedil;ado pelo caso de uso e o valor oferecido ao ator. Quando o nome do caso de uso &amp;eacute; anexado ao ator iniciador, uma frase significativa deve ser formada, por exemplo, Cliente retira dinheiro. Neste exemplo, &amp;apos;Cliente&amp;apos; &amp;eacute; o ator e &amp;apos;Retirar Dinheiro&amp;apos; &amp;eacute; o caso de uso.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1 Breve Descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o: Uma breve descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do prop&amp;oacute;sito do caso de uso e do valor oferecido aos seus atores.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1..N Fluxo B&amp;aacute;sico: Este &amp;eacute; o fluxo de eventos iniciado pelo ator e &amp;eacute; o caminho normal e esperado atrav&amp;eacute;s do caso de uso.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;0..N Fluxos Alternativos: S&amp;atilde;o fluxos adicionais de eventos que estendem o fluxo b&amp;aacute;sico para fornecer (i) formas alternativas de atingir o objetivo do caso de uso, (ii) comportamento opcional e (iii) tratamento de erros e exce&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Conte&amp;uacute;do adicional&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1..N Pr&amp;eacute;-condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es: Descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do estado em que o sistema deve estar antes que o caso de uso possa ser iniciado.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1..N P&amp;oacute;s-condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es: Descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do estado em que o sistema deve estar quando o caso de uso for conclu&amp;iacute;do.&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;1..N Requisitos Especiais: Declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de requisitos n&amp;atilde;o funcionais que se aplicam ao caso de uso.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Narrativa dos casos de uso&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:referenciaRE>&lt;table style=&quot;text-align: start;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;tbody&gt;
        &lt;tr&gt;
            &lt;td style=&quot;border: none;&quot;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;font-size: 1em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Refer&amp;ecirc;ncias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;sup style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; Modelagem de casos de uso, por Kurt Bittner e Ian Spence, Addison-Wesley Professional, Parte 2: Escrevendo e revisando descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de casos de uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;sup&gt;&lt;sup style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/sup&gt; Use Case Patterns and Blueprints, por Gunnar &amp;Ouml;vergaard e Karin Palmkvist, Addison Wesley, Cap&amp;iacute;tulo 13 Descrevendo Casos de Uso.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;
    &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:referenciaRE>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">9</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#NormaIsoIecIeee291482018 -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#NormaIsoIecIeee291482018">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PraticaDivida"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eParteDe rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#Identificacao"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:implementadaPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ConfrontarNormaProjetosEspecificados"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:classificacaoPratica>Geral</untitled-ontology-3:classificacaoPratica>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p&gt;A norma ISO/IEC/IEEE 29148:2018 descreve a qualidade dos requisitos desde a especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o at&amp;eacute; outras atividades de engenharia de requisitos no ciclo de vida do desenvolvimento de software.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Essa norma fornece detalhes para descrever requisitos textuais consistentes, incluindo caracter&amp;iacute;sticas, atributos e crit&amp;eacute;rios dos requisitos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A partir do momento que esses padr&amp;otilde;es de qualidade s&amp;atilde;o violados, podem surgir requirements semells e d&amp;iacute;vidas t&amp;eacute;cnicas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Analisar o documento de acordo com os projetos especificados e os requisitos documentados ajuda a identificar inconsist&amp;ecirc;ncias, baixos n&amp;iacute;veis de qualidade e viola&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e, consequentemente, identificar d&amp;iacute;vidas de requisitos.&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>Identificação através da ISO/IEC/IEEE 29148:2018</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#NotacoesModeloESR -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#NotacoesModeloESR">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloEspecificacaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2; text-indent: 36pt; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Poss&amp;iacute;veis nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que podem ser usadas para escrever requisitos do sistema&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;(Sommerville 2018):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Frases em linguagem natural:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Os requisitos s&amp;atilde;o escritos usando frases numeradas em linguagem natural. Cada frase deve expressar um requisito.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Linguagem natural estruturada:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Os requisitos s&amp;atilde;o escritos em linguagem natural em um formul&amp;aacute;rio ou modelo padr&amp;atilde;o. Cada campo fornece informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre um aspecto do requisito.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es gr&amp;aacute;ficas: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Modelos gr&amp;aacute;ficos complementados por anota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de texto, s&amp;atilde;o usados para definir os requisitos funcionais para o sistema; diagramas da UML (Linguagem de Modelagem Unificada), como diagramas de caso de uso s&amp;atilde;o comumente usados.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es matem&amp;aacute;ticas:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;Essas nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es s&amp;atilde;o baseadas em conceitos matem&amp;aacute;ticos como m&amp;aacute;quinas ou conjuntos de estado finito. Embora essas especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es inequ&amp;iacute;vocas possam reduzir a ambiguidade em um documento de requisitos, a maioria dos clientes n&amp;atilde;o entende uma previs&amp;atilde;o formal. Eles n&amp;atilde;o verificaram se ela representa o que querem e relutam em aceit&amp;aacute;-la como um contrato de sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px; font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Modelos gr&amp;aacute;ficos s&amp;atilde;o mais &amp;uacute;teis quando voc&amp;ecirc; precisa mostrar como um estado muda ou quando &amp;eacute; preciso descrever uma sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia de a&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Os diagramas de sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia e de estado da UML mostram a sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia de a&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que ocorrem em resposta a uma determinada mensagem ou evento. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;&apos; aria-level=&quot;2&quot;&gt;
        &lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: justify;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 12px;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es matem&amp;aacute;ticas formais s&amp;atilde;o algumas vezes usadas para descrever os requisitos para sistemas cr&amp;iacute;ticos de seguran&amp;ccedil;a, mas s&amp;atilde;o raramente usadas em outras situa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#OrientacoesER -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#OrientacoesER">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ProdutoTrabalhoPratica"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:contem rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#DefinicaoTecnicasER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:contem rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RealizacaoTecnicaER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eOrganizadoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#FonteInformacaoER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eOrganizadoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#TecnicaER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProduzidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PreparacaoTER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProduzidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RealizacaoER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Produto de Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:apresentacao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos caracterizando-se como a primeira atividade na constru&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma compreens&amp;atilde;o do problema que o software precisa resolver. Resumindo,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&amp;eacute; um processo de aquisi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de conhecimento, onde se aplicam t&amp;eacute;cnicas para compreender o neg&amp;oacute;cio a ser impactado pelo projeto de software, identificar as partes interessadas e para identificar e refinar os requisitos de software&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(V&amp;Aacute;ZQUEZ; SIM&amp;Otilde;ES 2016).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Eacute; limitado &amp;agrave; atividade humana, na qual as partes interessadas s&amp;atilde;o identificadas e os relacionamentos s&amp;atilde;o definidos entre o tempo de desenvolvimento e as partes interessadas, sendo um dos princ&amp;iacute;pios essenciais de um bom processo de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, uma comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o eficaz entre as v&amp;aacute;rias partes interessadas .&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;Informar o escopo do projeto &amp;eacute; considerado um elemento delicado da elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos, pois consiste em fornecer uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do software que est&amp;aacute; sendo especificado, sua finalidade e priorizar as entregas para garantir que as necessidades comerciais mais importantes do cliente sejam atendidas primeiro&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2014 )&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;No entanto, essas informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es iniciais minimizam o risco de especialistas em requisitos distribu&amp;iacute;dos em tempo elicitando requisitos de baixa import&amp;acirc;ncia ou aqueles pouco relevantes, quando o software &amp;eacute; entregue. Sobretudo, a descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o deve ser escal&amp;aacute;vel e extens&amp;iacute;vel para disposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de outros requisitos n&amp;atilde;o planejados inicialmente&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(SWEBOK 2014)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:apresentacao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Os requisitos de software podem ser obtidos de diferentes fontes e &amp;eacute; fundamental que as fontes potenciais sejam indicadas e comprovadas&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(SWEBOK 2024) &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Uma parte interessada pode ser qualquer pessoa, grupo ou organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Esteja participou diretamente no projeto;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Seja afetado pelo resultado do projeto;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Possa interferir no resultado do projeto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;As partes interessadas para projetos de software normalmente incluem (mas n&amp;atilde;o est&amp;atilde;o limitadas a essas):&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Clientes: Respons&amp;aacute;veis pela solicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e pagamento do software que ser&amp;aacute; desenvolvido &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;e/ou respons&amp;aacute;veis pela decis&amp;atilde;o se o produto de software ser&amp;aacute; colocado em produ&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Usu&amp;aacute;rios: Intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o direta ou indireta com o software e podem ser classificados em classes distintas de usu&amp;aacute;rios, como: usu&amp;aacute;rios que variam em frequ&amp;ecirc;ncia de uso, tarefas executadas, habilidade, n&amp;iacute;vel de conhecimento, prefer&amp;ecirc;ncias&amp;hellip;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Especialistas do dom&amp;iacute;nio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Equipe de opera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Equipe de suporte de produto de primeiro n&amp;iacute;vel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Oacute;rg&amp;atilde;os profissionais relevantes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ag&amp;ecirc;ncias reguladoras.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Grupos de interesse especial.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Desenvolvedores.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Classes de partes interessadas s&amp;atilde;o grupos de partes interessadas que possuem perspectivas e necessidades semelhantes. Trabalhar em um projeto de software em termos de classes de partes interessadas em vez de com partes interessadas individuais pode produzir insights importantes adicionais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Muitos projetos se beneficiam da realiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma an&amp;aacute;lise de partes interessadas para identificar o m&amp;aacute;ximo poss&amp;iacute;vel de classes de partes interessadas importantes. Isso reduz a possibilidade de que os requisitos sejam tendenciosos para partes interessadas mais bem representadas e para longe de partes interessadas menos bem representadas. A an&amp;aacute;lise das partes interessadas tamb&amp;eacute;m pode informar a negocia&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e a resolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de conflitos quando os requisitos de uma classe de partes interessadas entram em conflito com os requisitos de outra.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Outras fontes de requisitos que e n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;atilde;o partes interessadas, podem incluir:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Documenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, como requisitos para vers&amp;otilde;es anteriores, declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de miss&amp;atilde;o, conceito de opera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Outros sistemas;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Contexto empresarial que pode incluir pol&amp;iacute;ticas e processos organizacionais;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ambiente de computa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Pontos importantes na elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; (SWEBOK 2014)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Metas:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; Refere-se aos objetivos gerais de alto n&amp;iacute;vel do software. Os objetivos visam a motiva&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para o software, mas geralmente s&amp;atilde;o vagamente formulados. Engenheiros de software ou analistas de requisitos precisam ter aten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;agrave; proposta de valor (relativo &amp;agrave; prioridade) e ao custo dos objetivos. Realizar um estudo de solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es &amp;eacute; um mecanismo de baixo custo para atender a essa necessidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Conhecimento de dom&amp;iacute;nio:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; O engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos precisa compreender o dom&amp;iacute;nio do software. O conhecimento de dom&amp;iacute;nio fornece a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;base&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;necess&amp;aacute;ria para absorver todo o conhecimento de requisitos durante a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. As associa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es entre conceitos relevantes dentro do dom&amp;iacute;nio do aplicativo devem ser identificadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Partes interessadas:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; O engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos precisa identificar e gerenciar as percep&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de muitos tipos diferentes de partes interessadas quando necess&amp;aacute;rio, pois, &amp;agrave;s vezes, as partes interessadas podem entrar em conflito. Para minimizar esses conflitos, &amp;eacute; importante organizar reuni&amp;otilde;es regulares com as partes interessadas, oportunizando-lhes expressarem suas preocupa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para chegarem em um ponto comum a todos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Regras de neg&amp;oacute;cios:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Representam as declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que definem ou restringem algum aspecto da estrutura ou do comportamento do pr&amp;oacute;prio neg&amp;oacute;cio. Por exemplo: &amp;ldquo;Um aluno n&amp;atilde;o pode se registrar nos componentes curriculares do pr&amp;oacute;ximo semestre se houver pend&amp;ecirc;ncias de pagamento das mensalidades&amp;rdquo;. Essa regra de neg&amp;oacute;cio seria uma fonte de requisitos para o software de registro de cursos de uma universidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O ambiente operacional:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Os requisitos ser&amp;atilde;o definidos do ambiente para que o software seja executado. Como exemplos de ambientes operacionais, destacam-se, restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de tempo de software associadas ao tempo real ou restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de desempenho em um ambiente de neg&amp;oacute;cios. Estes devem ser produzidos porque podem variar de acordo com as op&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e o custo do software, assim como as restri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es &amp;agrave;s escolhas de design.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O ambiente organizacional:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O software geralmente &amp;eacute; desenvolvido para dar suporte a um processo de neg&amp;oacute;cios, cuja sele&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pode estar condicionada &amp;agrave; estrutura, cultura e pol&amp;iacute;tica interna da organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. O engenheiro de software ou analista de requisitos precisa ser sens&amp;iacute;vel a isso, pois um novo software n&amp;atilde;o deve importar mudan&amp;ccedil;as n&amp;atilde;o planejadas no processo de neg&amp;oacute;cios.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Orienta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es gerais voltadas &amp;agrave; elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">1</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


