        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Foram definidos um tipo de n&amp;oacute; para cada tipo de artefato, bem como as linhas que representam os tr&amp;ecirc;s tipos de relacionamento: &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;executado por&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;eacute; origem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;refinar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
