        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No planejamento da rastreabilidade de requisitos, devem ser definidas as seguintes informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es fundamentais:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informar o projeto, data e respons&amp;aacute;veis pela rastreabilidade de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Descrever a finalidade da rastreabilidade de requisitos, justificando sua necessidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informar o tipo de rastreabilidade de requisitos, conforme sua classifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informar os itens e/ou artefatos da rastreabilidade de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Definir o mecanismo para realizar a rastreabilidade de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Pode ser utilizada uma ferramenta de gest&amp;atilde;o para incluir essas informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre a rastreabilidade centralizando-a e a deixando vis&amp;iacute;vel para os membros do time de desenvolvimento.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Planejar a rastreabilidade de requisitos&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
