        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Devido a limita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de recursos das organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es direcionadas ao desenvolvimento de projetos de software, se torna invi&amp;aacute;vel capturar todas as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es conceb&amp;iacute;veis que possibilitam a rastreabilidade dos requisitos ao longo do ciclo de desenvolvimento do sistema &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(POHL; RUPP 2015).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para implementar a rastreabilidade de requisitos de maneira efetiva, as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es a serem registradas devem ser definidas conforme a sua&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;finalidade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Definir a rastreabilidade sem considerar uma finalidade clara, ter&amp;aacute; um impacto no resultado dessa atividade, pois as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es registradas podem n&amp;atilde;o ser proveitosas no projeto de desenvolvimento &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 8px;&quot;&gt;(POHL; RUPP 2015).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;Rastreabilidade de requisitos deve ser definida por finalidade&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
