        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Atividade Produto Trabalho&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ap&amp;oacute;s planejar as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es fundamentais da rastreabilidade de requisitos, deve-se registrar e especificar o v&amp;iacute;nculo entre os itens e/ou artefatos, conforme inicialmente planejado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Dependendo do mecanismo de representa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o adotado, pode-se utilizar ferramentas espec&amp;iacute;ficas para gerenciamento de requisitos apoiado na atividade de rastreabilidade de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;Realizar a rastreabilidade de requisitos&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">5</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">2</untitled-ontology-3:sequenciaAtividadeUC>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


    <!-- http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RecomendacoesModeloESR -->

    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RecomendacoesModeloESR">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PassosElementosPrática"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:estaContidoEm rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ModeloEspecificacaoRequisitos"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para evitar problemas de ambiguidade, requisitos vagos, Sommerville (2018) recomenda as seguintes diretrizes:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style=&quot;list-style-type: circle;&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Linguagem natural:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Estabelecer um formato padr&amp;atilde;o e garantir que todas as defini&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de requisitos sigam esse formato.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Padronizar o formato torna as omiss&amp;otilde;es menos prov&amp;aacute;veis e os requisitos mais simples de verificar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O formato deve expressar o requisito em uma &amp;uacute;nica frase.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Associe uma declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o justificativa a cada requisito do usu&amp;aacute;rio para explicar por que o requisito foi proposto.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A justificativa tamb&amp;eacute;m pode incluir informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre quem prop&amp;ocirc;s o requisito (a fonte do requisito) para identificar quem consultar se o requisito tiver que ser alterado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A hist&amp;oacute;ria do usu&amp;aacute;rio &amp;eacute; um padr&amp;atilde;o poss&amp;iacute;vel para registrar seus requisitos e necessidades recomendadas para organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es &amp;aacute;geis. Para que as hist&amp;oacute;rias do usu&amp;aacute;rio possam adotar o seguinte padr&amp;atilde;o&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Duarte 2021).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quem? O que? Para que?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Adotar uma linguagem consistente para distinguir entre requisitos obrigat&amp;oacute;rios e desej&amp;aacute;veis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Requisitos obrigat&amp;oacute;rios s&amp;atilde;o requisitos que o sistema deve suportar e geralmente s&amp;atilde;o escritos usando &amp;apos;deve&amp;apos;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Requisitos desej&amp;aacute;veis n&amp;atilde;o s&amp;atilde;o essenciais e s&amp;atilde;o escritos usando &amp;apos;pode&amp;apos;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Usar destaque de texto (negrito, it&amp;aacute;lico ou colorido) para destacar partes-chave do requisito.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;N&amp;atilde;o presuma que os leitores entendam a linguagem t&amp;eacute;cnica de engenharia de software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Eacute; f&amp;aacute;cil que palavras como &amp;apos;arquitetura&amp;apos; e &amp;apos;m&amp;oacute;dulo&amp;apos; sejam mal interpretadas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Deve-se, portanto, evitar o uso de jarg&amp;otilde;es, abrevia&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e acr&amp;ocirc;nimos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;/li&gt;
                &lt;/ul&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0c343d;background-color:#ffffff;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;Linguagem natural estruturada:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Linguagem natural estruturada &amp;eacute; uma maneira de escrever requisitos de sistema onde a liberdade do escritor de requisitos &amp;eacute; limitada e todos os requisitos s&amp;atilde;o escritos de uma maneira padr&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Essa abordagem mant&amp;eacute;m a maior parte da expressividade e compreens&amp;atilde;o da linguagem natural, mas garante que alguma uniformidade seja definida &amp;agrave; previs&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;As nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de linguagem estruturada utilizam modelos para especificar os requisitos do sistema.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda-se que os requisitos do usu&amp;aacute;rio sejam inicialmente escritos em cart&amp;otilde;es, sendo um requisito por cart&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Eles sugerem uma s&amp;eacute;rie de campos em cada cart&amp;atilde;o, como justificativa dos requisitos, como depend&amp;ecirc;ncias de outros requisitos, a fonte dos requisitos, materiais de suporte e assim por diante.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#0c343d;background-color:#ffffff;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;Sugest&amp;atilde;o de projeto padr&amp;atilde;o para elabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de projetos funcionais:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ou entidade sendo especificada.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de suas entradas e de onde elas v&amp;ecirc;m.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de suas sa&amp;iacute;das e para onde elas v&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que s&amp;atilde;o poss&amp;iacute;veis para a computa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ou outras entidades no sistema que s&amp;atilde;o usadas (a parte &amp;quot;solicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;quot;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da a&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; especificada.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Se uma abordagem funcional para uso, uma pr&amp;eacute;-condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o definindo o que deve ser verdadeiro a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;antes que a fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o seja chamada, e uma p&amp;oacute;s-condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o especificando o que &amp;eacute; verdadeiro depois &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;que a fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o para chamada.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos efeitos colaterais (se houver) da opera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O uso de especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es estruturadas remove alguns dos problemas de concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de linguagem natural.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A variabilidade na concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; reduzida e os requisitos s&amp;atilde;o organizados de forma mais eficaz. No entanto, ainda &amp;eacute; dif&amp;iacute;cil escrever requisitos de forma claros e inequ&amp;iacute;vocos, especialmente quando c&amp;aacute;lculos complexos (por exemplo, como calcular a dose de insulina) devem ser especificados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para resolver esse problema, voc&amp;ecirc; pode adicionar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es extras aos requisitos de linguagem natural, por exemplo, usando tabelas ou modelos gr&amp;aacute;ficos do sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
