    <owl:NamedIndividual rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#TecnicaER">
        <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#Alpha"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProgredidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ConfirmacaoInformacaoER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProgredidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PreparacaoTER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProgredidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RealizacaoER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:eProgredidoPor rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#RegistroInformacaoER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:possui rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#ExecutadoTecnicaER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:possui rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#FinalizadoTecnicaER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:possui rdf:resource="http://www.semanticweb.org/vivid/ontologies/2023/2/untitled-ontology-3#PlanejadoTecnicaER"/>
        <untitled-ontology-3:Icone>&lt;p&gt;Icone Alpha&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:Icone>
        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;T&amp;eacute;cnica de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos &amp;eacute; considerada como uma ferramenta para auxiliar o analista de requisitos na condu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da etapa de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o e compreens&amp;atilde;o dos requisitos do software (Reinher 2018).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Existem v&amp;aacute;rias t&amp;eacute;cnicas &amp;agrave; disposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o dos analistas de requisitos. Algumas t&amp;ecirc;m interven&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o humana e outras s&amp;atilde;o voltadas a outros tipos de fontes de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;_________________________________________&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Exemplos de t&amp;eacute;cnicas recomendadas para a elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Entrevista&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma das t&amp;eacute;cnicas mais populares para elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos a partir de fontes humanas. Consiste em uma conversa entre duas ou mais pessoas, envolvendo stakeholder e analista de requisitos, considerando um objetivo definido. A entrevista facilita o acesso &amp;agrave;s informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que, muitas vezes, est&amp;atilde;o apenas na mem&amp;oacute;ria das pessoas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Durante o contato, &amp;eacute; importante estabelecer uma conex&amp;atilde;o entre analista de requisitos e stakeholders, pois essa rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o permite maior seguran&amp;ccedil;a para expor quest&amp;otilde;es delicadas&amp;nbsp;(WIEGERS; BEATTY, 2013 apud REINHER 2018).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A entrevista, assim como qualquer outra t&amp;eacute;cnica, requer uma prepara&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o por parte de quem ir&amp;aacute; entrevistar. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda-se que o entrevistador, organize uma lista de quest&amp;otilde;es mais abrangentes no in&amp;iacute;cio e que, progressivamente, sejam mais detalhada:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;As quest&amp;otilde;es devem seguir uma sequ&amp;ecirc;ncia l&amp;oacute;gica e abordar um assunto de cada vez.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O roteiro com as quest&amp;otilde;es serve apenas para auxiliar o processo de entrevista, ou seja, n&amp;atilde;o deve ser restritiva, pois &amp;eacute; necess&amp;aacute;rio dar abertura para o entrevistado expor situa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, al&amp;eacute;m das questionadas inicialmente, relacionadas &amp;agrave; solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o que ser&amp;aacute; desenvolvida.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Sugere-se o uso de entrevista:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando as pessoas possuem o conhecimento necess&amp;aacute;rio sobre o neg&amp;oacute;cio e est&amp;atilde;o dispon&amp;iacute;veis para serem entrevistadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para ouvir as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es subjetivas (desabafos, sentimentos, pontos de vista) que podem ser &amp;uacute;teis para a defini&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos do sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para identificar e compreender o fluxo de trabalho e de documentos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Desafios durante a entrevista, pois pode n&amp;atilde;o obter os resultados desejados, caso ocorra uma das seguintes situa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Falta de expertise do condutor da entrevista.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Falta de preparo do entrevistado.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Tend&amp;ecirc;ncia do entrevistado em dar respostas desagrad&amp;aacute;veis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Tend&amp;ecirc;ncia do entrevistado em focar em palpites ou em respostas falsas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Resist&amp;ecirc;ncia do entrevistado com respostas &amp;ldquo;n&amp;atilde;o sei&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;n&amp;atilde;o conhe&amp;ccedil;o&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Orienta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para a condu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma boa entrevista:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Conquistar a confian&amp;ccedil;a do entrevistado se identificando e introduzindo claramente a finalidade da entrevista.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Documentar a entrevista, seja de forma textual ou gravando-a (o entrevistado deve autorizar a grava&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Analisar as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es expostas pelo entrevistado, criticamente, ap&amp;oacute;s a entrevista (n&amp;atilde;o corrija falhas, fa&amp;ccedil;a cr&amp;iacute;ticas ou discuta).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Iniciar com quest&amp;otilde;es mais abertas: &amp;ldquo;como &amp;eacute; o trabalho que voc&amp;ecirc; desenvolve na empresa?&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Evitar termos t&amp;eacute;cnicos e procurar se aproximar de termos familiares &amp;agrave; &amp;aacute;rea.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Evitar perguntas com respostas que possibilitam apenas &amp;ldquo;sim&amp;rdquo; ou &amp;ldquo;n&amp;atilde;o&amp;rdquo;, &amp;nbsp;pois limitam a participa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do entrevistado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Caso a entrevista se desvie do foco, reconduza, com habilidade.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Se o entrevistado se recusar a informar dados, obtenha o aux&amp;iacute;lio de outros colegas em papel semelhante ou, em &amp;uacute;ltimo caso, contacte o superior hier&amp;aacute;rquico do entrevistado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Esclarecer as poss&amp;iacute;veis preocupa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es manifestadas pelo entrevistado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Permitir espa&amp;ccedil;o para novos contatos, da sua parte e da parte do entrevistado.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Evitar interrup&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es nos relatos do entrevistado por parte do entrevistador.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Validar as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es obtidas com rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o ao objetivo definido.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Permitir que a entrevista seja conduzida de forma online, por meio de ferramentas de comunica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, caso o entrevistado tenha limita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de disponibilidade, embora, quando poss&amp;iacute;vel, realize-a presencialmente.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Garantir que a tecnologia (ferramenta, rede, internet) funcione adequadamente, evitando as interrup&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, que prejudicam a condu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da conversa.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;____________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Hist&amp;oacute;rias de usu&amp;aacute;rio ou user stories&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma user story deve conter apenas informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es suficientes para que os desenvolvedores possam produzir uma estimativa razo&amp;aacute;vel do esfor&amp;ccedil;o para implement&amp;aacute;-la.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O objetivo &amp;eacute; evitar parte do desperd&amp;iacute;cio que geralmente acontece em projetos onde requisitos detalhados s&amp;atilde;o coletados cedo, mas se tornam inv&amp;aacute;lidos antes do trabalho come&amp;ccedil;ar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Antes que uma&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;user story&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;seja implementada, um procedimento de aceita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o apropriado deve ser escrito pelo cliente para determinar se os objetivos da hist&amp;oacute;ria de usu&amp;aacute;rio foram cumpridos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(Massari 2016)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma boa user story deve ser objetiva, clara e direta, descrita ou relatada por um &amp;nbsp;stakeholder que precisa obter algum retorno de valor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Escrever a user story onde:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Algu&amp;eacute;m: Stakeholders&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quer o que: requisito&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para obter qual retorno: valor de neg&amp;oacute;cio&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Questione: &amp;ldquo;como esse requisito ser&amp;aacute; validado&amp;rdquo;?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Descreva a resposta como crit&amp;eacute;rio de aceita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da user story.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O exemplo no Quadro 1 de user stories do sistema da &amp;ldquo;ePlan services&amp;rdquo;, empresa que oferece planos de aposentadoria para pequenas empresas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quadro 1: Exemplo de us story e seus crit&amp;eacute;rios de aceita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;
    &lt;table style=&quot;border: none; border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;&quot;&gt;
        &lt;tbody&gt;
            &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td style=&quot;border: solid #000000 1pt;&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;User Story&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HU1&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;ldquo;Como usuário, posso pagar as taxas de manutenção do plano com cartão de crédito para que elas não sejam descontadas de meus rendimentos de aposentadoria l&amp;iacute;quidos&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp;(Cohn 2010).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Crit&amp;eacute;rios de aceita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&amp;nbsp;(&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Cohn&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;2010)&amp;nbsp;User Story HU1:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
                    &lt;ul&gt;
                        &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Aceitar Visa, MasterCard e American Express.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Não armazenar informações de cartão de crédito em nosso sistema.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                        &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Processar todas as transações de uma maneira segura.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
                    &lt;/ul&gt;
                &lt;/td&gt;
            &lt;/tr&gt;
        &lt;/tbody&gt;
    &lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Fonte: (Cohn 2010)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;_____________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Cen&amp;aacute;rios&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Consiste em uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de como o sistema pode ser utilizado em alguma tarefa particular. S&amp;atilde;o descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de exemplos de sess&amp;otilde;es de intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o com o usu&amp;aacute;rio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Os cen&amp;aacute;rios s&amp;atilde;o estruturados com informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es espec&amp;iacute;ficas mais detalhadas, coletadas, como entradas e sa&amp;iacute;das.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(Sommerville 2018)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um cen&amp;aacute;rio inicia com uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Durante o processo de elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, s&amp;atilde;o ampliados detalhes para representar uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o completa dessa intera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um cen&amp;aacute;rio pode incluir&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(Sommerville 2018)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do que o sistema e os usu&amp;aacute;rios esperam quando o cen&amp;aacute;rio se inicia.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do fluxo normal dos eventos no cen&amp;aacute;rio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do que pode dar errado e como esses problemas podem ser enfrentados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre outras atividades que poderiam acontecer ao mesmo tempo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do estado do sistema quando finaliza o cen&amp;aacute;rio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Exemplo de cen&amp;aacute;rio: Quando um aluno envia fotos para o KisTakePics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Figura 1: Exemplo de user stories&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXfN4CpOffiUcjmhDjI8N-lEQHghL6lp4pk3p1C9d5qKX3en2deFTKCraG6W78FTuENbGaiYQw6Wu3oKVjAtGwxXwM7gWcMEJqmK1-hMRSZOKyPbgg-7G7KcRmNxEgvaco8scsBAFja_1q_huP8evOfU9Laz?key=bWYZdeVOtJgVilXi-41QBQ&quot; width=&quot;314&quot; height=&quot;185&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61);font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Fonte: Sommerville, 2018&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;___________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;T&amp;eacute;cnica na qual o analista de requisitos permanece&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;in loco&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;para observar como ocorre o trabalho realizado pelos stakeholders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Consiste, n&amp;atilde;o apenas em ver e ouvir, mas em examinar fatos ou fen&amp;ocirc;menos que se deseja compreender. A observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pode ser usada para confirmar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es obtidas em outras t&amp;eacute;cnicas comparando-as com a realidade.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Eacute; poss&amp;iacute;vel acessar outras fontes de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es, como manuais de procedimentos e obter o fluxo de documentos ao longo das tarefas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o auxilia na percep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de ideias sobre pontos nos quais o projeto de software pode reduzir gargalos e reduzir trabalhos realizados de forma manual.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Sugere-se o uso &amp;nbsp;da observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o quando:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O fluxo de papeis &amp;eacute; relevante.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Problemas de desempenho impactam &amp;nbsp;a forma de executar o trabalho.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A influ&amp;ecirc;ncia do ambiente real &amp;eacute; necess&amp;aacute;ria.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Desafios da observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Um dos desafios e limita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; a interfer&amp;ecirc;ncia no ambiente de trabalho, mesmo sem ser intencional.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A presen&amp;ccedil;a de um observador, algu&amp;eacute;m externo &amp;agrave; empresa, pode provocar perturba&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es nas pessoas que pertencem aquele ambiente de trabalho, o que pode alterar as condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es reais em que o trabalho &amp;eacute; realizado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O observador tem seu pr&amp;oacute;prio ponto de vista, o que pode gerar impress&amp;otilde;es favor&amp;aacute;veis ou desfavor&amp;aacute;veis.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o consome um tempo significativo e, por conta disso, n&amp;atilde;o ser&amp;aacute; vi&amp;aacute;vel para ser utilizada em cada tarefa que o usu&amp;aacute;rio realiza.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O tempo de dura&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de uma observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pode variar, de acordo com o que se pretende observar.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Eacute; importante certificar-se que as tarefas ou fluxo que pretende observar, ocorrer&amp;aacute; durante o per&amp;iacute;odo da observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O observador deve registrar a sua percep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de forma discreta para n&amp;atilde;o atrapalhar o andamento das atividades laborais dos colaboradores da empresa.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Orienta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es durante a observa&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Como ocorre o fluxo de atividades entre os participantes do processo?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Existem momentos de pico de atividades?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Existem problemas causados pela tecnologia ou pela aus&amp;ecirc;ncia dela?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O que acontece quando a tecnologia falha (cai a rede, por exemplo)?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quais s&amp;atilde;o os fluxos alternativos e casos que requerem um tratamento especial?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;____________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Brainstorming&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;(Reinher 2018)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O brainstorming visa uma&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;ldquo;tempestade de ideias&amp;rdquo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;, sem cr&amp;iacute;ticas ou an&amp;aacute;lises, que ocorre em um ambiente informal, &amp;nbsp;descontra&amp;iacute;do e prop&amp;iacute;cio &amp;agrave; criatividade e &amp;eacute; uma t&amp;eacute;cnica que envolve um grupo de pessoas participantes.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Sugere-se o uso desta t&amp;eacute;cnica quando:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O ambiente da empresa &amp;eacute; informal e dispon&amp;iacute;vel para o desenvolvimento de atividades criativas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando pretende-se encontrar solu&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es inovadoras e criativas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando pretende-se lan&amp;ccedil;ar novos produtos no mercado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para realizar a t&amp;eacute;cnica de brainstorming, recomenda-se:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Providenciar o material com anteced&amp;ecirc;ncia e pode ser composto por post-it (notinhas adesivas coloridas), canetas para as anota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O material deve ser suficiente para todos os participantes terem acesso considerando os objetivos da t&amp;eacute;cnica.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A base do brainstorming &amp;eacute; a gera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de muitas ideias, e cada uma escrita em uma notinha.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A t&amp;eacute;cnica de brainstorming tamb&amp;eacute;m pode ser realizada por meio de ferramentas de apoio.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Fases do Brainstorming&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A se&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de brainstorming &amp;eacute; composta por tr&amp;ecirc;s fases:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Aquecimento:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Dedicada &amp;agrave; din&amp;acirc;mica selecionada, na qual o problema a ser resolvido ou a tem&amp;aacute;tica &amp;eacute; apresentada.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Idea&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;A idea&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o consiste na gera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de ideias manifestadas pelos participantes e anotadas nos post-it, vis&amp;iacute;veis a todos e sem julgamentos. Nesta fase um conjunto expressivo de ideias &amp;eacute; registrado pelos participantes. A fase de idea&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o finaliza quando o conjunto de ideias for suficiente para dar continuidade ao processo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Encerramento:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Ap&amp;oacute;s a idea&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, as ideias mais relevantes pelo grupo s&amp;atilde;o selecionadas e agrupadas e, ap&amp;oacute;s, &amp;eacute; dado continuidade ao processo de desenvolvimento adotado pela empresa. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Opcionalmente, pode ser realizada na &amp;uacute;ltima etapa, uma breve an&amp;aacute;lise ou vota&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o das melhores ideias.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Orienta&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Algumas quest&amp;otilde;es devem ser observadas para que o brainstorming seja realizado com sucesso:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;O brainstorming n&amp;atilde;o se aplica a grupos fechados e formais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;A t&amp;eacute;cnica requer um clima descontra&amp;iacute;do sem cr&amp;iacute;ticas e julgamentos, pois isso inibe o fluxo de ideias.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Quando o grupo for muito grande, o ideal &amp;eacute; fragment&amp;aacute;-lo em subgrupos com, no m&amp;aacute;ximo, 8 pessoas cada grupo, dependendo do contexto e dos perfis.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;___________________________________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Prototipagem&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Prot&amp;oacute;tipos s&amp;atilde;o representa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es visuais que se assemelham &amp;agrave;s informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que constar&amp;atilde;o no layout do software a ser desenvolvido.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Existem t&amp;eacute;cnicas de prototipagem, desde modelos de papel, de designs de tela, a vers&amp;otilde;es beta de produtos de software, sendo um forte mecanismo para elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos e para valida&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Prot&amp;oacute;tipos de baixa fidelidade s&amp;atilde;o frequentemente preferidos para evitar a &amp;ldquo;ancoragem&amp;rdquo; dos stakeholders em caracter&amp;iacute;sticas menores de um prot&amp;oacute;tipo de qualidade superior que pode limitar a flexibilidade do design de maneiras n&amp;atilde;o intencionais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10pt;font-family:&apos;Times New Roman&apos;,serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:descricao>
        <untitled-ontology-3:nome>&lt;p&gt;T&amp;eacute;cnicas para elicita&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos&lt;/p&gt;</untitled-ontology-3:nome>
        <untitled-ontology-3:sequencia rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal">7</untitled-ontology-3:sequencia>
    </owl:NamedIndividual>
    


