        <untitled-ontology-3:descricao>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;Para realizar a elabora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos recomenda-se definir e registrar informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es organizando-as por meio de um documento de concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify; font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;O quadro 1 apresenta uma sugest&amp;atilde;o de organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do documento de requisitos, que pode ser adaptada conforme a necessidade da organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o, do tipo de software que est&amp;aacute; sendo desenvolvido e da abordagem de desenvolvimento&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9px;&quot;&gt;(IEEE, 2018)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp; . &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;&amp;Eacute; &amp;nbsp;poss&amp;iacute;vel incluir informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre a evolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o prevista no sistema, pois ser&amp;aacute; &amp;uacute;til na manuten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do sistema&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; (Sommerville 2018).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 10pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Espera-se que:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;As informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es recomendadas podem ser registradas em documentos textuais ou ferramentas que fornecem o suporte para o registro e a rela&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o entre as informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;A abordagem de cada elemento descrito na recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da estrutura de organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do documento de concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos ser&amp;aacute; descrita ap&amp;oacute;s a apresenta&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;quadro1.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.2; text-indent: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 7pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;Quadro 1 - Recomenda&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es para o documento&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 8pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
