        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Introdu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Prop&amp;oacute;sito:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Deve apresentar o prop&amp;oacute;sito do software a ser especificado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Escopo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Deve considerar:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;a) identifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do produto de software a ser produzido pelo nome (por exemplo, Host DBMS, Report Generator, etc.);&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; b) explica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de que o produto de software far&amp;aacute;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; c) a aplica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do software que esteja sendo especificado, incluindo benef&amp;iacute;cios, objetivos e metas relevantes; e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; d) ser consistente com declara&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es semelhantes em especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de n&amp;iacute;vel superior (por exemplo, uma concep&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos de sistema), se existirem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Vis&amp;atilde;o do Produto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Perspectiva do produto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Definir o relacionamento do sistema com outros produtos relacionados. Considere um diagrama de blocos mostrando os principais elementos do sistema maior, interconex&amp;otilde;es e interfaces externas.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do produto:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Fornecer um resumo das principais fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que o software executar&amp;aacute;. Por exemplo, um programa de contabilidade pode usar esta parte para abordar a manuten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da conta do cliente, extrato do cliente e prepara&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de faturas sem mencionar a vasta quantidade de detalhes que cada uma dessas fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es requer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;Agrave;s vezes, o resumo da fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o necess&amp;aacute;ria para esta parte pode ser retirado diretamente da se&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o da especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de n&amp;iacute;vel superior (se houver) que aloca fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es espec&amp;iacute;ficas ao produto de software.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Casos de uso, hist&amp;oacute;rias de usu&amp;aacute;rios e cen&amp;aacute;rios tamb&amp;eacute;m s&amp;atilde;o usados para descrever as fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do produto.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: square; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Para fins de compreens&amp;atilde;o:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; a) as fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do produto devem ser organizadas de forma que tornem a lista de fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es gratuitas para o adquirente ou para qualquer outra pessoa que esteja lendo o documento pela primeira vez.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;b) m&amp;eacute;todos textuais ou gr&amp;aacute;ficos podem ser usados para mostrar as diferentes fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e seus relacionamentos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Caracter&amp;iacute;sticas do usu&amp;aacute;rio:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;D&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;escrever as caracter&amp;iacute;sticas gerais dos grupos pretendidos de usu&amp;aacute;rios do produto, revelando caracter&amp;iacute;sticas que influenciam a usabilidade, como n&amp;iacute;vel educacional, experi&amp;ecirc;ncia, defici&amp;ecirc;ncias e conhecimento t&amp;eacute;cnico. Esta descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o deve declarar os motivos pelos quais certos requisitos espec&amp;iacute;ficos s&amp;atilde;o especificados posteriormente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Limita&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; fornecemos uma descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o geral de quaisquer outros itens que limitam as op&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es do fornecedor, incluindo:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;a) requisitos e pol&amp;iacute;ticas regulat&amp;oacute;rias;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;b) especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de hardware (por exemplo, requisitos de temporiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de sinal);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;c) interfaces para outros aplicativos;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;d) opera&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o paralela;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;e) fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de auditoria;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;f) fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de controle;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;g) requisitos de linguagem de ordem superior;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;h) protocolos de handshake de sinal (por exemplo, XON-XOFF, ACK-NACK);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;i) requisitos de qualidade (por exemplo, confiabilidade);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;j) criticidade do aplicativo;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; k) considera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de seguran&amp;ccedil;a;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; l) considera&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es f&amp;iacute;sicas/mentais; e&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;m) especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es originadas de outros sistemas, incluindo requisitos em tempo real do sistema controlado por meio de interfaces.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Requisitos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Defini&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos do usu&amp;aacute;rio: Descreva&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;os servi&amp;ccedil;os fornecidos ao usu&amp;aacute;rio. Os requisitos n&amp;atilde;o funcionais do sistema tamb&amp;eacute;m devem ser descritos nesta se&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o. Esta descri&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o pode usar linguagem natural, diagramas ou outras nota&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es que sejam compreens&amp;iacute;veis para os clientes. Os padr&amp;otilde;es de produto e processo que devem ser seguidos devem ser especificados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Especifica&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de requisitos de sistemas:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Descrever os requisitos funcionais e n&amp;atilde;o funcionais em mais detalhes. Se necess&amp;aacute;rio, outros detalhes tamb&amp;eacute;m podem ser adicionais aos requisitos n&amp;atilde;o funcionais. Interfaces para outros sistemas podem ser acrescentadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Modelos de sistemas:&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Pode incluir modelos gr&amp;aacute;ficos de sistema mostrando os relacionamentos entre os componentes do sistema, o sistema e seu ambiente. Exemplos de modelos poss&amp;iacute;veis s&amp;atilde;o modelos de objetos, modelos de fluxo de dados ou modelos de dados sem&amp;acirc;nticos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Arquitetura do sistema:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Este item deve apresentar uma vis&amp;atilde;o geral de alto n&amp;iacute;vel da arquitetura planejada para o sistema, mostrando a distribui&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es entre os m&amp;oacute;dulos do sistema. Os componentes reutilizados devem ser destacados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; color: rgb(12, 52, 61); font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Evolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do sistema:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Descrever as suposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es fundamentais nas quais o sistema &amp;eacute; baseado e quaisquer mudan&amp;ccedil;as antecipadas devido &amp;agrave; evolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do hardware, mudan&amp;ccedil;as nas necessidades do usu&amp;aacute;rio e assim por diante. Esta se&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; &amp;uacute;til para projetistas de sistemas, pois pode ajud&amp;aacute;-los a evitar decis&amp;otilde;es de design que restrinjam mudan&amp;ccedil;as futuras prov&amp;aacute;veis no sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
        &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Ap&amp;ecirc;ndices:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Fornecer informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es detalhadas e espec&amp;iacute;ficas relacionadas ao sistema que est&amp;aacute; sendo desenvolvido. Por exemplo: autoridade de hardware e banco de dados. Os requisitos de hardware definem como configura&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es m&amp;iacute;nimas e ideais para o sistema. Os requisitos do banco de dados definem a organiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o l&amp;oacute;gica dos dados usados pelo sistema e pelos relacionamentos entre os dados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;ul style=&quot;font-size: initial;&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: circle; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
                &lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;Gloss&amp;aacute;rio: &amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&apos;color: rgb(12, 52, 61); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;deve definir os termos t&amp;eacute;cnicos usados no documento. N&amp;atilde;o deve-se expor suposi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sobre a experi&amp;ecirc;ncia ou conhecimento do leitor.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
            &lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;/ul&gt;
    &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li style=&apos;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 12px; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;&apos;&gt;
